dcterms:creator: A. Krizhevsky
I. Sutskever
G. E. Hinton
dcterms:description: The MNIST dataset consists of handwritten digits, commonly used for training various image processing systems. In this paper, it is used to evaluate the performance of the proposed CNN model with patch reordering on distorted versions of the dataset.
dcterms:title: MNIST

dcterms:creator: A. Krizhevsky
I. Sutskever
G. E. Hinton
dcterms:description: ImageNet-2012 is a large-scale dataset consisting of images from 1000 classes, used for image classification tasks. The dataset is utilized to test the performance of the proposed model on large-scale image recognition tasks.
dcterms:title: ImageNet-2012

dcterms:creator: D. Nister
H. Stewenius
dcterms:description: UK-Bench is an image retrieval benchmark dataset that includes groups of images from different viewpoints of the same object or scene. It is used to evaluate the proposed model's performance in image retrieval tasks.
dcterms:title: UK-Bench
